# drum shell (type 2, FRICPW) + co-rotating end covers (type 3, CAPFRIC):
# two meshes, one wall fix, both rotated in stage 2
fix drum all mesh/surface file ${MESH} type 2
fix drum all mesh/surface file ../../../templates/meshes/drum_r0.075_l0.050.stl type 2
fix caps all mesh/surface file ${CMESH} type 3
fix caps all mesh/surface file ../../../templates/meshes/drum_caps_r0.075_l0.050.stl type 3
fix drumwall all wall/gran model hertz tangential history rolling_friction epsd2 mesh n_meshes 2 meshes drum caps
